Here is a 1-2 line summarization of the Gujarati couplet in English:

The pure-hearted saint, Shyama, reveals the divine truth; 
Through his vision, sinners like us can gain liberation from all our misdeeds.

Here is a summary of the Gujarati couplet in English:

The bride's laughter echoes joyfully, and so do the tears of the groom; 
The wedding celebration is filled with merriment, as the newlyweds are made to dance together.
